" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Nasal encephalocele",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 288px; height: 287px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Nasal cephaloceles are herniations of brain, meninges, and/or cerebrospinal fluid through a defect in the skull. Those containing brain tissue are termed encephaloceles. They may communicate with the subarachnoid space and, occasionally, the ventricular system. The arrow points to&nbsp;an encephalocele&nbsp;underneath the nasal dorsum.",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
"    </div>",
